comment: /**  * A list holding the configured data formats  */
code: /**  * A list holding the configured data formats  */ public void setDataFormats(List<DataFormatDefinition> dataFormats) {     this.dataFormats = dataFormats. }

comment: /**  * @return A Map of the contained DataFormatType's indexed by id.  */
code: /**  * @return A Map of the contained DataFormatType's indexed by id.  */ public Map<String, DataFormatDefinition> asMap() {     Map<String, DataFormatDefinition> dataFormatsAsMap = new HashMap<>().     for (DataFormatDefinition dataFormatType : getDataFormats()) {         dataFormatsAsMap.put(dataFormatType.getId(), dataFormatType).     }     return dataFormatsAsMap. }
